window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Gameshouse is an unusual institution. Many know it as the place where fortunes can be made and lost though games of chess, backgammon - every game under the sun.</p> <p>But a select few, who are picked to compete in the higher league, know that some games are played for higher stakes - those of politics and empires, of economics and kings...</p> <p>And now, the ultimate player is about to step forward.</p>"; 
